{"tid":598854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日媒：外相下月訪港　望港嚴查船舶　防朝鮮避制裁","createTime":"2018-03-20T02:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T04:29:20.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2d030bb3a6112489e11230729439f94886571d4","tid":598854,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T02:10:56.000Z","msg":"共同社報道，昨天（19日）從日本政府相關人士獲悉，外相河野太郎已著手協調本月下旬訪問香港的事宜。他將與香港特別行政區行政長官林鄭月娥舉行會談，確認就嚴格履行船舶檢查採取合作以防朝鮮逃避制裁。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，此行瞄準預計4、5月舉行的韓朝及美朝首腦會談，力爭就維持壓力直至朝鮮採取無核化具體行動的重要性達成共識。<br />\n<br />\n共同社提到，去年12月曾發現香港註冊船舶在海上將精煉石油產品轉移至朝鮮籍船舶。<br />\n<br />\n河野還將要求撤銷香港在東日本大地震後對日本產食品實施的進口限制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%97%A5%E5%AA%92-%E5%A4%96%E7%9B%B8%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E8%A8%AA%E6%B8%AF-%E6%9C%9B%E6%B8%AF%E5%9A%B4%E6%9F%A5%E8%88%B9%E8%88%B6-%E9%98%B2%E6%9C%9D%E9%AE%AE%E9%81%BF%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%259C%259B%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259A%25B4%25E6%259F%25A5%25E8%2588%25B9%25E8%2588%25B6-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259C%259D%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E9%2581%25BF%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%2F&d=C88rzUCsV2hIq0hYYhme%2Ff%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=4ae288ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%259C%259B%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259A%25B4%25E6%259F%25A5%25E8%2588%25B9%25E8%2588%25B6-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259C%259D%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E9%2581%25BF%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%2F&h=891a91ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%97%A5%E5%AA%92-%E5%A4%96%E7%9B%B8%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E8%A8%AA%E6%B8%AF-%E6%9C%9B%E6%B8%AF%E5%9A%B4%E6%9F%A5%E8%88%B9%E8%88%B6-%E9%98%B2%E6%9C%9D%E9%AE%AE%E9%81%BF%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81/</a>"},{"pid":"8cf1ba4cbd5e27aed642c5725135325110a56685","tid":598854,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T02:35:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab9e5257f659e775b7575c9a83d8dd75f8ea9bc8","tid":598854,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T02:37:45.000Z","msg":"架仔咁撚串"},{"pid":"5430e91d3685d15fffc597e7cead752981dfc26d","tid":598854,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"小日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34915aa77196dceaa62629574f4563db36b64179","tid":598854,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5430e91d3685d15fffc597e7cead752981dfc26d","tid":598854,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"小日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T04:29:20.000Z","msg":"信唔信林鄭讚多幾句習大大，唔想接見小日本<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}